metadata.name: Imaginary Holiday
metadata.description:
I dreamed that I was walking in a colorful world that is different from the gray world which I live in.
 In the rainbow world I saw  humans and creatures who lived in happiness and hope and I saw all my interests there. I don't like to wake up from this colorful dream. I wish my gray world were as colorful as my dreams...
Resolution: 5000 x 6000 px
